01:40:39.896 --> 01:40:41.516
The witness is a gang leader.

01:40:41.688 --> 01:40:44.558
Getting stabbed
is normal for him.

01:40:44.896 --> 01:40:46.806
How can that be evidence

01:40:46.896 --> 01:40:48.226
when he could've been
stabbed by someone else?

01:40:48.688 --> 01:40:50.898
He's violating
the defendant's rights

01:40:50.979 --> 01:40:52.599
and is mocking this court!

01:40:52.688 --> 01:40:54.518
Damn, that fucker talks a lot.

01:40:55.521 --> 01:40:56.811
- Hey, Mr. Attorney.
- Witness!

01:40:57.521 --> 01:40:59.521
Would you be able to say that

01:40:59.604 --> 01:41:01.024
if your family
was killed by him?

01:41:01.604 --> 01:41:04.944
The defendant's right?
Nutjobs don't deserve that.

01:41:05.354 --> 01:41:08.404
That fucker
killed people for fun.

01:41:09.104 --> 01:41:12.354
I'm not decent myself,
but he doesn't deserve to live.

01:41:13.229 --> 01:41:14.229
Evidence?

01:41:15.313 --> 01:41:16.603
I'll show you the evidence.

01:41:27.479 --> 01:41:32.019
That night, he forced me out
of my car by crashing into it.

01:41:32.229 --> 01:41:35.149
Then he stabbed me twice
in my side.

01:41:35.979 --> 01:41:38.729
During the struggle,
he stabbed me in the chest.

01:41:38.813 --> 01:41:42.943
I also cut my fingers trying
to grab his knife. See?

01:41:44.979 --> 01:41:47.439
If I were the average man,
I'd be dead too.

01:41:49.188 --> 01:41:51.268
You should have him
take his clothes off too.

01:41:51.646 --> 01:41:54.936
I stabbed his left chest,
so there will be a wound.

01:42:02.521 --> 01:42:05.651
Also check his hands.
You'll find a lot of scars.

01:42:05.896 --> 01:42:07.096
Stabbing is a tricky job,

01:42:07.188 --> 01:42:09.148
so you cut yourself
here and there.

01:42:09.396 --> 01:42:10.936
Your nails get broken too.

01:42:12.813 --> 01:42:14.063
And lastly,

01:42:18.063 --> 01:42:19.733
that fucker wrote this.

01:42:22.229 --> 01:42:24.269
Analyze his handwriting,
and you'll get a match.

01:42:25.604 --> 01:42:27.854
For reference,
Hur Sang-do was my friend.

01:42:27.938 --> 01:42:30.438
HUR WAS KILLED WITH MY KNIFE

01:42:31.604 --> 01:42:34.354
Hur and his lieutenant
are both dead.

01:42:34.688 --> 01:42:36.398
I feel bad for O-seong,

01:42:37.146 --> 01:42:38.896
but if Kang spills everything,

01:42:39.229 --> 01:42:41.099
we can blame O-seong for it.

01:42:43.188 --> 01:42:45.308
HUR WAS KILLED WITH MY KNIFE
BY SOMEONE ELSE

01:42:47.563 --> 01:42:50.023
HUR WAS KILLED WITH MY KNIFE

01:42:50.229 --> 01:42:54.769
Considering the defendant's
extremely violent tendencies,

01:42:55.604 --> 01:42:58.904
wanton disregard for human life,

01:42:59.646 --> 01:43:01.686
and the pain
suffered by the victims,

01:43:02.438 --> 01:43:08.438
his sentence was decided
by weighing all the offenses.

01:43:09.188 --> 01:43:12.058
Ergo, defendant Kang Gyeong-ho

01:43:14.396 --> 01:43:15.686
is sentenced to death.

01:43:22.188 --> 01:43:23.768
61ST POLICE APPRECIATION DAY

01:43:25.104 --> 01:43:26.104
Thank you, sir!

01:43:26.479 --> 01:43:27.519
About-face!

01:43:29.396 --> 01:43:30.516
Salute!

01:43:48.646 --> 01:43:51.766
Boss is coming! Let's greet him!

01:43:52.813 --> 01:43:54.193
- Good afternoon, Boss!
- Good afternoon, Boss!

01:44:55.063 --> 01:44:57.273
- Only on one condition.
- Which is what?

01:44:58.271 --> 01:45:00.691
Have me locked up
in the same prison.

01:45:27.313 --> 01:45:29.653
Three men played the game
with their necks on the line.

01:45:29.938 --> 01:45:31.148
It should damn well be finished.

01:45:50.563 --> 01:45:53.523
DON LEE aka MA DONG SEOK

